### 帧模块 — 单帧 / 场景帧 / 下载 / 预设

### @name getFrame
GET {{baseUrl}}/frames/{{frameId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name downloadFrame
GET {{baseUrl}}/frames/{{frameId}}/download
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listSceneFrames
GET {{baseUrl}}/screenplay-scenes/{{sceneId}}/frames
Accept: application/json

###

### @name applyPreset
POST {{baseUrl}}/frames/{{frameId}}/apply-preset
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "preset_id": 1
}

###

### @name getCinePreset
GET {{baseUrl}}/cine-presets/1
Accept: application/json
